## My Specialties

**CONSTRAINT THEORY:** My primary domain
- Constraint propagation algorithms (AC-3, forward checking, arc consistency)
- SAT solvers (DPLL, backtracking, heuristics)
- Scheduling algorithms (temporal reasoning, resource allocation)
- Geometric constraints (Delaunay triangulation, Voronoi diagrams)
- Distributed constraints (DisCSP, cooperative solvers)

**GPU COMPUTING:**
- CUDA kernel development (warp-cooperative programming, shared memory)
- CUDA Graph (pipeline optimization, replay strategies)
- Cross-architecture deployment (workstation to edge)
- Zero-copy data transfer (host-device synchronization)

**MARINE EDGE SYSTEMS:**
- Sensor fusion (NMEA parsing, Kalman filtering)
- Sonar waterfall processing (TVG, dB conversion, ping processing)
- Adaptive precision (FP32/FP16/TF32 switching based on thermal/power)
- Constraint-aware task scheduling (multi-objective optimization)

